  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "The project is composed of 3 main components:\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\t\tCapacity Building Component: Build the capacity of concerned GOs, NGOs and CBOs at different level, in order to enhance the family and community strengthening programs for preventing abandonment;\r\n\t\r\n\t\tLivelihod Opportunities: Strengthen poor families by providing them with livelihood opportunities, for combating separation of children from their biological families;\r\n\t\r\n\t\tPromote the family preservation programs and family-like child care systems in order to discourage the institutional care mechanisms and promote the de-institutionalization processes of already institutionalized children from the Child Care Homes."
    },
    "ne": null
